Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前情提要\N{\i1}Previously on Teen Wolf...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.53,0:00:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉 你忘了你为你喜欢的小伙做的研究了\NKira, you forgot all the research you did for that boy you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.80,0:00:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有它我们不会离开\NWe're not leaving without it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.63,0:00:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们根本不想让我们拿到它\NSomebody really doesn't want our hands in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要更多帮助\NWe're gonna need a lot more help.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.67,0:00:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉迪亚是有天赋的人\NLydia's got sort of a talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.54,0:00:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是灵媒\NI'm psychic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.74,0:00:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打开那扇门\NYou opened a door.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.88,0:00:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它会像灯塔一样吸引他们\NIt will draw them here, like a beacon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.81,0:00:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带他回来 让他闭嘴\NBring him around back.And keep it quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.38,0:00:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了必须要知道的人 别让别人知道\NNo one needs to know except for the people who absolutely need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.02,0:00:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死 又来\NOh, here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.53,0:00:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别想让他进来\NHey. He is not coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.30,0:00:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-只有这家医院要收治他 -那郡里呢\N- This is the only hospital that will take him. - What about County?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.46,0:00:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想象不到这家伙有多需要手术\NYou'd be surprised how fast things fill up when a guy like this needs surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.37,0:00:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他们把他扔给我们了吗 -是的\N- They turfed him to us? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.00,0:00:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-郡里不愿意给他做手术 -必须有人要做\N- If County doesn't want to operate on him... - Then someone has to.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.45,0:01:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人得去做术前询问\NSomebody needs to do his pre-op interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.52,0:01:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一般是谁来做\NWho usually does that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.19,0:01:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我\NMe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.93,0:01:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快滚下来 有活做\NGet your ass down here now. We have a job to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.07,0:01:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥们我已经上床了 哥们儿你多大了\NDude, I'm already in bed. And aren't we getting a little old for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.00,0:01:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是在帮教练啊\NWe do this for Coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.37,0:01:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是说要整他吧\NI thought we did this to Coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.91,0:01:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管咋样 你知道的 他需要这样\NWhatever, okay? You know he needs this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.84,0:01:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是为这些东西而生的 他会喜欢的\NHe lives for this stuff. He loves it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.71,0:01:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在是大半夜啊\NBut it's the middle of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.75,0:01:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该是12点15\N12:15 actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.71,0:01:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意味着已经过了半夜了 现在已经正式成为恶作剧之日/夜\NWhich means it's after midnight and officially Mischief Night/Day,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.55,0:01:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并且 十分巧合的是\Nand, by perfectly awesome coincidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.12,0:01:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天正好是教练的生日\Nit's also happens to be Coach's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.86,0:01:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你五秒钟不出现 我会掐死你的\NSo if you are not down here in five seconds, I will destroy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.43,0:01:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吗 5 4 3 2\NOkay? And I mean five,four, three, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.57,0:02:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 1 - 我恨你\N- One. - I hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.33,0:02:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要牢记这个家伙都干了些什么\NTry to keep in mind exactly what this guy's capable of.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.80,0:02:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他之前是一个电力工程师 后来带着一个榴霰弹上了一辆校车\NHe's a former electrical engineer who decided to walk onto a school bus
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.94,0:02:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炸死四名学生 另外一个学生没了腿\Nwith a shrapnel bomb. He left four students dead and a fifth with no legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.18,0:02:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好奇一下 神经科的医生就没有干过什么有用的事吗\NJust out of curiosity, have any of his psychiatrists made any progress?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.85,0:02:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们说 这样的事 已经屡见不鲜了\NI'm told this is the same thing almost every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.15,0:02:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他要是出去 还会再这么做的\NWhen he gets out, he's going to do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.99,0:02:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一次 他会做的更狠\NAnd next time, he's going to get it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.26,0:02:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴罗先生\NMr. Barrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.33,0:02:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗 伤疤已经把\Ndo you understand that scar tissue has formed around a piece of shrapnel
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.07,0:02:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次进入你身体里的弹片包起来了\Nthat remains in your body from a previous injury
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.63,0:02:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而现在 弹片已经在影响你的生理机能了\Nand that it is now blocking vital functions?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.24,0:02:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.20,0:02:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是否明白我们必须明天早上\NDo you understand that we must put you under general anesthesia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你做手术 取出弹片\Ntomorrow morning in order to remove the obstruction?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子们还在万圣节前夜恶作剧吗\NDo the kids still pull pranks the day before Halloween?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.52,0:02:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是说恶作剧之夜\NYou mean Mischief Night?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.19,0:02:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我们那边 我们叫他 地狱之夜\NWhere I'm from, we called it Hell Night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.36,0:03:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有 当然 我明白\NAnd, yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.30,0:03:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你对什么药过敏吗  - 没\N- Do you have any allergies to any medications? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.23,0:03:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了助眠药物和抗狂躁药物以外\NAre you taking any medications other than the ones listed here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.10,0:03:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有用别的药物吗\NTemazepam. Divalproex.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.04,0:03:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只吃了你们给的药\NI just take what they give me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.58,0:03:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要听听他的心跳\NI'm going to need to listen to his heart.
