Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吸气\NIn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.62,0:04:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你不把你最想问的问题问了呢\NWhy don't you just ask the question you really want to ask?
