Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.60,0:05:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回学校了\NYou're back in school?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.33,0:05:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 只是找你谈谈\NNo, just to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哟 这不像你们的行事风格啊\NOh. That's kind of a change of pace for you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.14,0:05:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们不是最爱掰胳膊 折腿 杀戮的吗\NUsually, you're just hurting, maiming, and killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.87,0:05:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你需要一个狼群 我们需要一只头狼\NYou need a pack. We need an Alpha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.21,0:05:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在搞笑么 当然不行\NYeah. Absolutely not. That's hilarious though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.21,0:05:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你来找我们帮忙 我们帮了\NYou came to us for help. We helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.01,0:05:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们把他的脸打成了肉酱\NYou beat his face into a bloody pulp.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.85,0:05:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是帮助 在我看来 你们是在害他\NThat's not helping. In my opinion, that's actually counter-productive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.42,0:05:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为啥我要同意\NWhy would I say yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的力量增强了 我们的加入会让你更有实力\NWe'd add strength. We'd make you more powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.02,0:05:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有理由拒绝\NThere's no reason to say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么没有 你们抓着德里克的爪子\NI can think of one. Like the two of you holding Derek's claws
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后卡莉抓着博伊德插死了她\Nwhile Kali impaled Boyd.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.63,0:05:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事实上 我现在就想插死他们\NIn fact, I don't know why we're not impaling them right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.97,0:06:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想试试\NYou want to try?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.44,0:06:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 他们不相信你\NSorry, but they don't trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.54,0:06:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也一样\NAnd neither do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.02,0:06:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在咋办\NWhat now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.09,0:06:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 想都别想\NNo. No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.40,0:06:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们还没毕业呢 -我们不需要\N- We never finished. - And we don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.50,0:06:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我想呢?\NWhat if I want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.14,0:06:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你...你真的想回到高中吗?\NYou... You seriously want to go back to high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.44,0:06:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是莉迪亚的原因吗?\NIs this about Lydia?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.64,0:06:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是想让斯科特改变主意\NThis is about getting Scott to change his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.18,0:06:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们连二等狼都不是了 我们只是低等狼\NWe're not just Betas anymore. We're Omegas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.24,0:06:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还记得那些贱人吗?\NThe bitches, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当被我们欺负的人发现我们已经没有狼群了\NWhen everyone we've screwed over finds out we don't have a pack anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.35,0:06:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得会怎什么样?\Nwhat do you think's going to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们死定了\NWe're dead on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.09,0:06:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这总比回到高中好\NThat's still better than being back in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会的 没门\NI'm not doing it. No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.67,0:07:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不上数学课\NI'm not taking math.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.14,0:07:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我替你上\NI'll take it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.48,0:07:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看着点 别砸脸!\NAll right, that's my face!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.72,0:07:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 基友 好决定\NHey, dude, good decision, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.79,0:07:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老大明智的决定\NGood Alpha decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.42,0:07:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望吧\NI hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.52,0:07:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 你知道的\NNo, you know so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在看什么?\NWhat are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我  - 是你啊\N- Me? - You.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.87,0:07:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在看她?\NYou looking at her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.47,0:07:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她\NHer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.77,0:07:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪个她\NWho her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.07,0:07:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个她 基拉 你喜欢她吗?\NHer her. Kira. You like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.77,0:07:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我...\NNo. I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.01,0:07:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 嗯 她不错啦 新来的\NYeah, yeah, she's okay. She's new.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.85,0:07:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就约她出去啊\NSo, ask her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.95,0:08:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在?\NNow?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.42,0:08:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 现在\NYes, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.82,0:08:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 现在? - 现在\N- Right now? - Right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.29,0:08:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯科特 你还没懂我的意思\NScott, I don't think you get it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.32,0:08:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是阿尔法 你是食物链顶端的人\NYou're an Alpha. You're the apex predator.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.76,0:08:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都喜欢你 你就像人人都喜欢的女神一样\NEveryone wants you. You're like the hot girl that every guy wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.13,0:08:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女神\NThe hot girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是最正的女神\NYou are the hottest girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.77,0:08:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是女神\NI'm the hot girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.57,0:08:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 你是\NYes, you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.71,0:08:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整我啊\NPeek-a-boo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.04,0:09:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们就这点儿能耐\NThat's all you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.95,0:09:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不够看\NThat's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.46,0:09:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你妈逼\NSon of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.53,0:09:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恶作剧之夜 恶魔之夜\NMischief Night, Devil's Night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.76,0:09:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不管你怎么叫它\NI don't care what you call it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.47,0:09:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们小崽子都是恶魔\NYou little punks are evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.77,0:09:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得每次万圣节我家被砸鸡蛋很搞笑吗?\NYou think it's funny every Halloween my house gets egged?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.51,0:09:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个男人的房子就应该像他的城堡一样\NA man's house is supposed to be his castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的特么像个煎蛋饼一样\NMine's a frickin' omelet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.62,0:09:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 还有 你们又要来一遍\NOh, this? We're gonna do this again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.22,0:09:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不会上当\NI don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.43,0:09:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生日快乐\N"Happy Birthday."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.90,0:10:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"爱你 格林伯格"\N"Love, Greenberg."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在干嘛?\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.98,0:10:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有苍蝇\NThere's a fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.60,0:10:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人觉得我应该划个小口\NAnybody else here think I should make a minor slip
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.14,0:10:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让这家伙在手术台出血死掉吗?\Nand let this bastard bleed out on the table?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.98,0:10:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这只是一个手术玩笑而已 梅丽莎 放轻松\NThat's just a little surgical humor, Melissa. Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.91,0:10:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我 手术钳\NClamp, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.68,0:10:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吸盘\NSuction
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我们看看里面有什么\NLet's see what we have here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.73,0:11:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦!\NOh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.40,0:11:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 这...这...这肯定不是弹片\NOkay, that's... That's... That's not shrapnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.86,0:11:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,额 10号刀 10号刀\NUh, 10 blade. 10 blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10号刀 好吗\N10 blade, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.87,0:11:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了 你把10号刀弄掉了\NWhat's the problem? You're missing your 10 blade?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.74,0:11:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,医生...医生 你来看看这个\NDoctor... Doctor, I think you should see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.44,0:11:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的觉得你该来看看这个\NI really think you should see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.79,0:11:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走开！走开！\NMove! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.76,0:11:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他跑了 巴罗跑了\NHe's gone. Barrow's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.00,0:11:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他没事的 别死啊\NHe's going to be okay. Stay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.13,0:11:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗷! 你还有麻醉剂吗?\NOw! Don't you have any anesthetic?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.66,0:11:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有\NYep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.97,0:11:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 你至少要告诉我在冒什么险掏什么吧\NWell, are you at least going to tell me what I risked life and digit for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.87,0:12:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你等下看就知道了\NI'm going to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.92,0:12:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,火灾后 她就只剩这么多了\NAfter the fire, that's all that was left of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.22,0:12:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特丽雅 我真不知道\NTalia. I can't decide
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.56,0:12:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该说这是感人还是有病\Nif that's touching or morbid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.63,0:12:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我猜真正的问题是\NI guess the real question is,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.00,0:12:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你准备拿他们干嘛\Nwhat are you planning on doing with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.26,0:12:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要问她一点事\NI have to ask her something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.90,0:12:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,据我所知\NAnd from what I've heard,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是唯一可行的方法\Nthis is the only way it's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.01,0:12:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你特么在逗我\NYou gotta be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.77,0:12:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得我干嘛要把你的指头缝上\NWhy do you think I sewed your finger back on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.35,0:12:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警长 警长\NSheriff? Sheriff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.75,0:12:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\NHey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.55,0:12:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些苍蝇来自巴罗的肿块\NThese dead flies everywhere They came out of Barrow. Out of his tumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.29,0:12:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样\NIs that even possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.95,0:12:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蛆会从身体里爬出来 这叫蛆虫病\NMaggots can come from the body. It's called myiasis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.79,0:12:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是从胃里 这不太像\NBut from the stomach? It's not likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.63,0:12:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有\NAnd there's something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.19,0:12:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚 他告诉我他为什么杀了那些小孩\NLast night, he told me why he killed those teenagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.53,0:13:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 我读了那篇报道 发光的眼睛\NYeah, I know. I read the report.Glowing eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.06,0:13:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们知道有这种年轻人\NWe know a few kids that fit that description.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.33,0:13:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着 被偷的救护车找到了\NListen up, everyone. The stolen ambulance has been spotted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.10,0:13:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在杜鲁门和斯波尔丁街角\NCorner of Truman and Spaulding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.00,0:13:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,离学校只有三个街区\NThat's three blocks from the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.67,0:13:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快 我们走\NLet's go. Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.91,0:13:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逗我吧\NOh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.18,0:13:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝对没可能\NI don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.18,0:13:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你别以为在你杳无音讯两个周后突然出现\NThere's no way you come back here after two weeks of nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.59,0:13:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带着你可爱的笑容 棕色的研眼睛\Nwith your cute little smile, the dark eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宽宽的额头 发达的肌肉\Nthe brooding forehead, the muscles,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就会再跟你在教练的办公室啪啪啪\Nand suddenly we're ripping each other's clothes off in Coach's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.43,0:13:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 这不会发生的\NNo way. It's not gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.68,0:13:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,导员的办公室咋样\NGuidance office?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.08,0:13:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 等等 威廉姆斯·巴罗\NWait a minute, wait a minute! The William Barrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.11,0:14:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霰弹恐怖分子 就在这附近\NThe Shrapnel Bomber? Spotted nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.85,0:14:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事实上比附近更近一些\NA little closer than nearby, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.82,0:14:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地下室怎么走\NHow do we get down to the basement?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.65,0:14:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要知道每一个入口的位置\NI need to know where every entrance is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.29,0:14:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到时候没有人能够自由进出\NI don't want anybody coming in or out of the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.26,0:14:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老爸 这里发生了什么\NDad, what's really going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.83,0:14:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴罗在找那些眼睛发光的人\NBarrow went after kids with glowing eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.53,0:14:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的原话是什么\NHe said those exact words?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.20,0:14:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 没人知道他是怎么从麻醉状态里醒来的\NYeah. And no one knows how he woke up from anesthesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.53,0:14:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们剖开他 发现了一个装满苍蝇的肿瘤\NJust that when they opened him up, they found a tumor full of live flies,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.34,0:14:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那场面一定很了不起\Nwhich in any other circumstance would be all kinds of awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.71,0:14:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是说苍蝇\NDid you say flies?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.44,0:14:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉迪亚\NLydia?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.71,0:14:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最近总是听到奇怪的声音\NAll day I have been hearing this sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.91,0:14:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像\NIt's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.11,0:15:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗡 嗡的\NThis buzzing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.35,0:15:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像是苍蝇的声音吗\NLike the sound of flies?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.58,0:15:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是苍蝇的声音\NExactly like the sound of flies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.39,0:15:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道为啥你坐在这陪着我\NAll I'm saying is, I don't understand why you're sitting here with me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.09,0:15:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不去餐厅找你的朋友玩\Ninstead of in the cafeteria with the other kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.39,0:15:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是我只是想陪陪你\NMaybe I want to keep you company.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.59,0:15:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同学看到你和我一起 你该觉得不好意思 别陪我了\NYou should be embarrassed to be seen with me. Not keeping me company.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.13,0:15:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡拉\NKira?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.50,0:15:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你必须去交朋友\NYou must have some friends by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.50,0:15:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道我是咋回事 我在家有很多朋友的\NI don't know what's wrong with me. I had a lot of friends back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.61,0:15:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是在这 每次我一张嘴\NBut here it's like every time I open my mouth,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.64,0:15:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像一个傻瓜一样 说话不着边际了\NI just start rambling like an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.18,0:15:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屡败屡战 总好过\NTry again. Fail again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,止步不前\NFail better.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.98,0:15:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是萨缪尔·贝克特的话吗\NAre you quoting Samuel Beckett to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.15,0:15:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我记得是犹大的话\NI thought that was Yoda.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.69,0:15:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总会有人喜欢你的\NSomeone will show an interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.76,0:15:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是一个漂亮的孩子\NYou're a beautiful girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.53,0:15:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁会拒绝你\NHow could they not?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一一个喜欢我的是一个疯狂的狼\NThe only one who's shown any interest in me is a rabid coyote.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也许可以与狼共舞\NMaybe you could date the coyote?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.03,0:16:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要约会 更不需要男朋友\NI don't want a date. And I definitely don't need a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.61,0:16:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想交朋友\NI just want to make a few friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.54,0:16:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿哥们 你死哪去了\NHey, dude, where the hell have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.05,0:16:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警察走了\NThe police are leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.88,0:16:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们为啥走\NWhy are they leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.38,0:16:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警察吗\NThe police?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.35,0:16:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那意味着他们搜查完了 他不在这里\NThey must have cleared the building and grounds, which means he's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.09,0:16:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-谁 你们到底在说...  -他一定在这里\N- Who? What are you guys... - He has to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.43,0:16:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那声音... 那苍蝇声\NThat sound... The buzzing I've been hearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.76,0:16:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越来越响了\NIt's getting louder.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.16,0:16:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有多响\NHow loud?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.02,0:16:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸\NDad! Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.52,0:16:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩\NYeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.52,0:16:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们不能走\NYou can't leave yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.12,0:16:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有目击者说他在火车站\NWe got an eyewitness that puts Barrow by the train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,0:16:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 咱们走 斯特林斯基  - 等一下爸爸\N- Let's go, Stilinski. - Whoa, whoa.Dad, please just...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.49,0:16:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉迪亚说他还在这里\NLydia said that he's still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她看见了吗\NDid she see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.76,0:16:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确切的说 没有\NNot exactly. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.26,0:16:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但也不是完全没有 她有感觉的\NWell, not at all actually. But she has a feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.40,0:16:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超自然的感觉\NA supernatural feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.04,0:16:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉迪亚不是棋子啊\NLydia wasn't on the chessboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:16:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在是了\NShe is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.97,0:17:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 变形怪 -不 是报丧女妖\N- Kanima? - Um, Banshee.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 哦 天哪 - 我知道这有多疯狂\N- Oh, God. - I know. I know how it sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.54,0:17:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大致上就是 他能感觉到有人快死了\NBut basically it means that she can sense when someone's close to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.78,0:17:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他感觉的到我要杀了你吗\NCan she sense that I'm about to kill you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.62,0:17:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.48,0:17:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 看\NAll right, look,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.45,0:17:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说我不相信你\NI'm not saying I don't believe,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.22,0:17:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在我更相信目击者\Nbut right now, I'm going with eyewitness over Banshee.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.32,0:17:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会留一些人的 学校封锁到三点\NWe're leaving a few deputies here. The school's on lockdown till 3:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.56,0:17:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没人出入\NNobody comes in, nobody goes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.69,0:17:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老兄 这是我现在能做的\NBuddy, that's the best I've got right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.46,0:17:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能最大能提供的 斯泰尔斯\NThat's the best I can give you, Stiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.43,0:17:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把我留在这里 这不是...这是最糟糕的\NYou're leaving me here, that is not... That is the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.07,0:17:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿到了吗?\NYou got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答应我 小心点\NPromise me you'll be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.01,0:17:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到这个人的眼神了 很恐怖的\NI looked right in this guy's eyes, and it was terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.58,0:17:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 好的 妈 我保证\NYeah. Okay, Mom,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.02,0:17:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吗 小心\NOkay? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.89,0:17:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉迪亚认为他还在这\NLydia thinks that he's still here even though
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.56,0:17:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警察搜遍了全校\Nthe cops searched the whole school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.83,0:17:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我们有一件他们没有\NBut they didn't have one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.36,0:17:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我们的嗅觉\NOur sense of smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.30,0:18:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动物图鉴整整有一千多页\NThe Bestiary is literally 1,000 pages long.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.57,0:18:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们要在这些文件里找到任何有关尸体\NIf I'm going to find anything about flies coming out of people's bodies,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.20,0:18:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可要花上我整个晚上\Nit could take me all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.37,0:18:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,记得吗\NAnd remember, the word
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.51,0:18:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苍蝇在古拉丁语是{\i1}musca.{\i}\Nin archaic Latin for fly is {\i1}musca.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.64,0:18:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了\NGot it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.11,0:18:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们从哪里开始\NWhere do we start?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.88,0:18:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,楼上\NUpstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.42,0:18:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须走了\NWe gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在怎么办\NSo this is how it's gonna be now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.72,0:18:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们信任他们吗\NWe trust them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.39,0:18:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我让他们帮我们并不意味我相信他们\NJust because I'm letting them help, doesn't mean I trust them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.66,0:18:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好吧 我也不相信他们\NYeah, well, I don't trust them either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.90,0:18:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者有好感\NOr like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.87,0:18:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,实际上 我对他们恨之入骨\NIn fact, I hate them and just want them to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.20,0:18:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 如果巴罗在这里并有自己的计划的话 你就放开做吧\NWell, if Barrow's actually here and he's\Ngot a plan, you might get what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.55,0:18:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你发现什么了吗\NYou got something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.09,0:19:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,几个意思\NOh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.93,0:19:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯科特和艾塞克在地下室 是吗\NScott and Isaac are in the basement, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 和伊桑和埃登在一起 计划是在中间\NYeah, with Ethan and Aiden. The plan is we meet in the middle,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.57,0:19:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,锅炉房碰头\Nin the boiler room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.45,0:19:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有的狼人\NAll of the wolves...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.95,0:19:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛会发光的\NAll of the ones with glowing eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.92,0:19:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都在地下室的锅炉房\Nare in the basement at the boiler room?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.62,0:19:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 天呐\NOh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.16,0:19:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个王师傅可以用锅炉房炸掉整个学校的\NAn engineer could use a boiler room to blow up the whole school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.23,0:19:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须让他们离开那里\NWe have to get them out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.66,0:19:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须撤离所有人\NWe have to get everyone out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.90,0:19:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们该怎么做\NHow do we do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.19,0:20:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在恶作剧之夜拉响火灾警报就算了\NPulling a fire alarm on Mischief Night is one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.99,0:20:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在谋杀现场旁边这么做你疯了吗!\NDoing it when there's a mass murderer spotted nearby is insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是四年前的我 我揍死你了\NIf I was four years younger, I'd punch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.73,0:20:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 教练 这不科学\NWhat? Coach, that doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,额 我觉得科学得很\NOh, well, it does to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里\NThere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.81,0:20:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们什么也没找到\NWe didn't find anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.05,0:20:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至气味都没有\NNot even a scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.45,0:20:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在三点钟了 学校放学了\NIt's 3:00, so school's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.62,0:20:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果这里有个炸弹 他会现在引爆吗\NIf there was a bomb, wouldn't he have set it off by now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.65,0:20:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是不是意味着大家安全了\NDoes that mean everybody's safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.09,0:20:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.96,0:20:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就...\NI just...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.61,0:21:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你声音放的多大?\NHow loud are you playing that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.34,0:21:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧!快离开这里!\NLet's go! Get the hell out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.19,0:21:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗 这种仪式总会有点危险\NYou know, there's always an element of danger to rituals like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.43,0:21:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我实际上并不赞成这么做\NI'm not particularly fond of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.50,0:21:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除非他们可以让我\NUnless they somehow
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.67,0:21:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从中受益\Nbenefit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.74,0:21:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想要什么?\NWhat do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.87,0:21:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想留着他们\NI want to keep them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.94,0:21:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情感价值\NSentimental value.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.08,0:21:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是你妈妈 也是我的姐姐(妹妹)\NShe was your mother, but she was also my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.31,0:21:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 我就不能有一点情绪吗\NWhat? Am I not allowed a little bit of sentiment?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.34,0:22:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 太慢了 -不 不 等等\N- Too long. - No! No, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.69,0:22:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉\NKira?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.16,0:22:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备吃饭吧 穿漂亮点\NGet ready for dinner. And put on something nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.30,0:22:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我穿漂亮干嘛?\NWhy would I need to wear something nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.30,0:22:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我邀请了一个客人参加我称之为\NI invited a guest for what I like to call the.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.01,0:22:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"险些让我女儿成为野狼晚餐的感恩餐"\N"Thank You for Saving My Daughter from Becoming a Coyote Dinner" dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.91,0:22:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好\NHey.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.08,0:22:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 天辣\NOh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.69,0:23:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯科特 我确信作为一个本地的加州人\NSo, Scott, I'm sure that as a native Californian,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.92,0:23:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定在日式寿司餐厅吃过\Nyou've eaten at some pretty impressive Japanese sushi restaurants.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.56,0:23:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我可以告诉你我老公是很棒的主厨\NBut I have to tell you that my husband is a superb chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.90,0:23:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我们有惊起一油金鱼 海胆 鱼子和比目鱼\NOkay, we have hamachi, uni, ikura, and hirame.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.51,0:23:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以前没有吃过寿司吗 是吗\NYou've never eaten sushi before, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.18,0:23:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们都是生的吗\NIs it all raw?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.11,0:23:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,饭除外\NNot the rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.08,0:23:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 我们应该今晚吃意式千层面的\NOh, my God, guys. We were supposed to have lasagna tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.78,0:23:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只不过想让他留下个印象 我不想把这...\NI was trying to impress him. I didn't want to bring out the...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.92,0:23:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那什么 我马上去做意式千层面\NYou know what? I'll make lasagna.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.16,0:23:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 不 不用了 我可以 我可以尝试任何东西 真的\NOh, no, no! It's okay. I can try anything. Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.26,0:23:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.77,0:23:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里 试着像握铅笔一样\NHere. Try holding this one like a pencil.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.71,0:24:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个指头放在下面 像这样 另一个放在上面\NAnd this one goes under it, like this. Then you just move the top one,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.22,0:24:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 像 像这样...  - 嗯 谢谢\N- like, like this... - Yeah. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.48,0:24:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寿司?\NSushi?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.56,0:24:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不同颜色的线是什么意思?\NWhat do the different colored strings mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.49,0:24:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 代表不同的调查阶段\NOh, just different stages of the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.53,0:24:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绿色是解决了 黄色是待定 蓝色是快...\NSo green is solved, yellow is to\Nbe determined, blue's just pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.27,0:24:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 红色是什么意思 - 没解决的\N- What does red mean? - Unsolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.44,0:25:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,墙上只有红色的\NYou only have red on the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.80,0:25:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 谢谢 我知道\NYes, I'm aware. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.77,0:25:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你拉警报被扣留了么\NDid you get detention for pulling the alarm?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.34,0:25:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 这星期每天都会 不要紧啦 我们在调查事情嘛\NYep. Every day this week. It's okay, though. We were onto something.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.15,0:25:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尽管我们没发现什么巴罗在那里的证据\NEven though we couldn't find any proof of Barrow being there?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.29,0:25:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 莉迪亚\NHey, Lydia.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.22,0:25:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次发生什么的时候你总是对的 不是吗\NYou've been right every time something like this has happened, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.33,0:25:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以不要怀疑你自己了\NSo don't start doubting yourself now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.73,0:25:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有气味 没有炸弹\NNo scent. No bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.44,0:25:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并且我麻烦你了\NAnd I got you in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.94,0:25:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事 听着 巴罗在那里 好吗\NOkay, look. Barrow was there. All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.34,0:25:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的 你感觉到了 不是吗\NYou knew it. You felt it. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.91,0:25:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着 如果你想的话 我可以现在马上回学校查一晚上\NAnd look, if you wanted to, I'd go back to\Nthat school right now and search all night
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.55,0:25:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来证实他\Njust to prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.20,0:26:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起来 快起来 我们去学校\NGet up. Get up now. We're going to the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.79,0:26:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带电的窗户\NElectrified the windows?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.50,0:26:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\NYep.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.53,0:26:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想说点什么吗?\NDidn't wanna say anything about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.50,0:26:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-不想  -好吧\N-Nope. -Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.10,0:26:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你来这干嘛\NWhat are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.57,0:26:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你可以多一双眼睛\NI figured you could use an extra pair of eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.98,0:26:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你懂拉丁语\NCan you read Latin?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.05,0:26:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不懂 但是我可以看图片\NNo. But I can look at pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.80,0:27:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这肯定不是我的颜色\NThat's not exactly my color.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.17,0:27:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这极其疼的\NThis is going to be excruciatingly painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.44,0:27:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快做吧\NJust do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.88,0:27:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会的 我只是说一下\NOh, I'm going to. I just wanted you to know
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.58,0:27:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都有一点小报复\Nwe all have our petty revenges.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.55,0:27:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们从纽约搬到这来的\NSo you guys moved here from New York?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.19,0:27:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我家几代都在这里\NI have family ties here. Several generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.66,0:27:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幸村是日本人 是吗\NYukimura is Japanese, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.39,0:27:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是的\NMmm-hmm. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.96,0:27:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我实际上是韩国人 我和妻子结婚后\NYes, but I'm actually Korean. When my wife and I married,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.23,0:27:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟她姓 因为他是她们家唯一的幸存者\NI took her name, as she was the only surviving member of her family.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.43,0:27:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不想跟姓两个吗\NYou didn't want to take both names?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.14,0:27:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日本的婚姻法律规定\NWe were married in Japan, where the law says that the couple
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.11,0:27:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们只能有一个姓 姓{\i1}koseki{\i}\Nmust share the same name. To belong to the same {\i1}koseki.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.37,0:28:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我妻子的血统很独特 实际上我准备在课堂上讨论它的\NMy wife's lineage is quite unique. I was actually going to discuss it in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.18,0:28:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊\NPlease don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.55,0:28:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉 你应该对你的遗传感到自豪\NKira. You should be proud of your heritage.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.82,0:28:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能够融入你妈妈的家庭很荣幸\NIt was a profound honor to join your mother's family.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.49,0:28:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯科特? 你的芥末怎么了\NScott? What happened to your wasabi?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.36,0:28:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为这是色拉酱\NI thought it was guacamole.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.67,0:28:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们在找啥\NSo what are we looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.47,0:28:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那玩意儿好像是锁着的\NThat was supposed to be locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.87,0:28:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊我知道 还发现什么别的了么\NYeah. I know. Notice anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.17,0:28:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闻起来像化学试剂\NIt smells like chemicals.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.58,0:28:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们就不会追寻到他的气味了\NThey wouldn't have been able to catch his scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.06,0:28:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他曾在这儿给自己动了个小手术\NHe was here, performing very minor surgery on himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.20,0:28:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说得对\NYou were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.47,0:28:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是为什么我感觉不妙\NThen why don't I feel good about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.04,0:29:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许是因为他在这儿杀了人\NProbably because he was here to kill somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.74,0:29:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁 我们必须找出是谁\NBut who? That's what we gotta figure out.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.84,0:29:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们分头行动 找找线索\NWe could spread out, start looking for... Anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.05,0:29:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉迪亚 那些是什么\NLydia, what are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.22,0:29:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,化学原子序数\NAtomic numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.23,0:29:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是分子式吗\NIs it a formula?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.63,0:29:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是 19号元素是钾 53号元素是碘 88号元素是镭\NNot really. 19's potassium. 53's iodine. 88's radium.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.80,0:29:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前两种元素生成了碘化钾\NThe first two make potassium iodide...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.17,0:29:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你确定是钾吗\NPotassium is K?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.81,0:29:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,源自于拉丁文Kalium 科学上管这叫拉丁语名\NFrom kalium, the scientific neo-Latin name.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.61,0:29:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,镭是什么\NWhat's radium?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.35,0:29:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-A.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.06,0:30:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉\NKira.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.66,0:30:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我刚吃了寿司 老妈\NYes, Mom. I ate sushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.49,0:30:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都不知道你会使筷子了\NI didn't even know that you could use chopsticks.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.46,0:30:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 老妈 我想问你点事  -说吧\N- Mom, can I ask you something? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.27,0:31:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么不 你为什么不把姓换回成德尔加多\NWhy didn't you... How come you never changed your name back to Delgado?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.94,0:31:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么保留了你父亲的姓吗\NDo you mean, why did I keep your father's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.84,0:31:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是啊  - 好吧 因为那也是你的姓 亲爱的\N- Yeah. - Yeah. Because it's your name, too, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.95,0:31:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得走了 宝贝儿 行么 我爱你\NI gotta go, sweetheart, okay? I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.82,0:31:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 感谢上帝 我可不是故意的\NOh, thank God. No offense to sushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.16,0:31:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵 也许我们应该先招待你一些加州寿司卷才对\NYeah, we probably should have started you out on California rolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.92,0:31:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到什么了么\NYou find anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.89,0:31:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一份文献说苍蝇可以给死人传递信息\NThere's a reference about flies being able to carry messages to the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.63,0:32:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你呢\NWhat about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.69,0:32:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴力西卜 苍蝇之王\NOh, just... Beelzebub, the Lord of the Flies.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.18,0:32:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你确定\NAre you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.95,0:32:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.45,0:32:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是想吻我\NYou were just trying to kiss me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.49,0:32:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的\NNo, I wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.32,0:32:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你要干嘛 用头撞我么\NThen what were you trying to do? Head-butt me?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.09,0:32:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 也许我真的想吻你\NAll right, maybe I was trying to kiss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.53,0:32:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你脱线了吧\NAre you completely, totally out of your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.56,0:32:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的以为我会吻你吗\NYou actually think that I would want to kiss you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.47,0:32:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者 或者说再吻其他的狼人\NOr... Or any other werewolf again?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.13,0:32:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信我 我是绝对不会吻你的\NBecause trust me on this, I would never kiss you. Ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.21,0:32:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 绝不  - 绝不 好吧 行\N- Never. - Never. Okay. All right, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.08,0:32:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不也不会亲你\NI won't kiss you either.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.36,0:33:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉森 来我办公室\NAllison. Can I see you in my office?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.40,0:33:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把枪放哪儿了\NWhere I keep my guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.68,0:33:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是和狼人\NAnother werewolf?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.25,0:33:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看见她了吗 你问了什么\NDid you see her? What did you ask her?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.32,0:33:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她有提到我吗\NDid she say anything about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.36,0:33:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我操 情况不妙啊\NWell, that doesn't look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.77,0:33:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 谢谢你的晚餐  - 是谢寿司还是披萨\NThanks for dinner.For the sushi or the pizza?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.87,0:33:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵 披萨不错\NUh... The pizza was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.91,0:34:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看起来不错啊帅哥\NYou seem like a really nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.71,0:34:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只因为是你救了我\NAnd not just because you kept me from getting eaten by a coyote.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.29,0:34:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还做了什么\NDid I do something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.06,0:34:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你记得我的名字\NYeah. You remembered my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.21,0:34:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯科特\NScott!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.85,0:34:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯科特 快醒醒\NScott? Scott!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.95,0:34:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴罗带走了科拉\NBarrow, he took Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.96,0:34:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们知道 他一直跟着她\NWe know. He was after her the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.53,0:34:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没有 只有有关苍蝇和死人的东西\NNo, nothing. Just stuff about flies and the dead. Nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.93,0:34:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 谢谢\NAll right, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.27,0:34:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得想办法 他会杀了她的\NWe have to think of something. He's going to kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.13,0:34:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道他在那 我咋知道的\NI knew he was there. How did I know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.77,0:34:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你听见苍蝇了是吗\NBecause you heard the flies, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.34,0:34:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在听见了啥\NWhat do you hear now?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.94,0:35:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没 我觉得我能帮上忙\NNothing. I feel like I can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.71,0:35:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不知道咋做\NBut I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.91,0:35:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 就像是话都到嘴边了 我就是不知道该怎么说\NIt's like it's on the tip of my tongue,\Nand I don't know how to trigger it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.05,0:35:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只想尖叫... 我对天发誓 我是真的真的想大叫\NI just... I swear to God, it literally makes me want to scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.59,0:35:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 那就叫出来吧\NOkay, then scream. Lydia, scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.36,0:35:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没苍蝇了\NIt's not flies.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.23,0:36:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是电流\NIt's electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.67,0:36:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等下 巴罗是电力工程师\NWait a second, Barrow was an electrical engineer.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.47,0:36:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在变电站工作\NHe worked at a power substation.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.24,0:36:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪个变电站\NWhat substation?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.92,0:36:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在干嘛\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.16,0:36:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在 现在么\NRight now? Ah. Right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.83,0:36:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要给你照张相\NI'm gonna take your picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.40,0:36:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是证明我们在一起\NJust a little proof of our time here together.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.60,0:36:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,证明给那些不相信的人\NA little proof for all of those people who never believed.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.58,0:36:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 照了 可以让我走了么\NOkay, you got your picture. You want to let me go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.62,0:37:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看过 诅咒的村庄 这部电影吗\NDid you ever see a movie called Village of the Damned?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.76,0:37:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原版的 不是再制版的 没人在意再制版的\NThe original. Not the remake. Nobody cares about crappy remakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.69,0:37:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说1960年的那部经典黑白片\NI'm talking about the 1960 black-and-white masterpiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.97,0:37:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拍的是那些有着漂亮头发\NIt's about this group of children. Blonde-haired,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.64,0:37:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯美的少年\Nbeautiful children
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.74,0:37:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们的眼睛能发光\Nwho can make their eyes glow.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.05,0:37:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们做很坏很坏的事\NAnd they do terrible, terrible things.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.75,0:37:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海报上写着他们的口号\NThe tag line on the poster read,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.82,0:37:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“当心他们麻痹了世人的的眼睛”\N"Beware the stare that will paralyze the will of the world."
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.26,0:37:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我告诉你们我看见了眼睛发光的孩子\NNow, when I told everyone that I saw children with glowing eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.50,0:37:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们不相信我 我想让他们行动起来\Nthey wouldn't believe me. I tried to get them to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.30,0:37:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他们不关心 不在意\NBut they wouldn't budge. They wouldn't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.04,0:37:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像他们已经被麻痹了\NAs if they had been paralyzed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.22,0:38:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要把人们从麻痹中叫醒\NI am going to shake them out of their paralysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.79,0:38:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要让他们行动起来 我要\NI'm going to get them moving. I'm going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.89,0:38:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要电醒他们\NI am going to galvanize them.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.83,0:38:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 等着 等警察来\NOkay. Wait here, all right? Just wait for the cops to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.81,0:38:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为啥要我等\NMe? Wait, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.08,0:38:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只拿了一个棒\NI only got one bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.32,0:38:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯科特 不要\NScott! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.42,0:38:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心\NLook out!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.80,0:38:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别 你要... 你要找的不是她\NDon't... She's not... She's not the one you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.72,0:39:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别\NNo...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.36,0:39:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要\NDon't.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.16,0:39:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停下来 不要\NStop! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.51,0:40:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾萨克 艾萨克\NIsaac! Isaac!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.88,0:40:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾萨克 快开门\N- Isaac! - Isaac, come on, open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.08,0:40:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾萨克 快开门\N- Isaac! - Isaac, open up!
